			<tr>
			<td>45652</td><td>API Endpoints &quot;Get settings - update settings&quot;</td><td>Get Settings


GET /admin/settings
Return grouped settings.Only accessible by Admin role.


🔹 Update Settings (Per Section)


PUT /admin/settings/{group}
Validate payload.Update multiple keys inside that group.Return updated data.


🔹 Toggle Setting Status


PATCH /admin/settings/{key}/toggle
Switch is_active state.Return updated status.

