			<tr>
			<td>45676</td><td>[Admin-2] user story  Admin Control over Merchant and Supplier Access</td><td>As an admin,
I want to manage the status of merchants and suppliers (suspend or block),
So that suspended users can login but have restricted actions, and blocked users are prevented from logging in or causing issues with ongoing orders.

Acceptance Criteria:


When a merchant is suspended, they can login but cannot add products to cart or proceed to checkout.When a supplier is suspended, they can login but their products are hidden from the website.When a merchant is blocked, they cannot login.When a supplier is blocked, if they have ongoing orders, they cannot be blocked until the orders are completed.
