			<tr>
			<td>45774</td><td>[Admin-3] user story Admin  Manage Academic Structures Master Data</td><td>Title:

Admin can manage Academic Year, Subject, Curriculum Track, and Accrediting Bodies


As a

System Administrator

I want to

Add, edit, and activate/deactivate Academic Years, Subjects, Curriculum Tracks, and Accrediting Bodies

So that

I can manage the academic master data dynamically from the admin panel without developer intervention.


📌 Acceptance Criteria

1️⃣ Common Requirements for All Modules

Applies to:


Academic Year (السنه الدراسيه)Subject (المواد)Curriculum Track (المسار التعليمى)Accrediting Bodies (جهات الاعتماد)

Add


Admin can create a new record.Admin must enter:
Name (Arabic) – requiredName (English) – required
System validates required fields.System saves record with Active = true by default.

Edit


Admin can edit:
Name (Arabic)Name (English)
Changes are saved successfully.Validation rules apply on edit.

Toggle Status


Admin can toggle status between:
ActiveInactive
Status change is reflected immediately in listing.Inactive records should not appear in public-facing or dependent dropdowns.

Listing


Admin can view paginated list.Admin can see:
Name (Arabic)Name (English)Status (Active / Inactive)Actions (Edit / Toggle)


Search &amp; Filter


Admin can search by:
Arabic nameEnglish name
Admin can filter by:
ActiveInactive

