			<tr>
			<td>46364</td><td>Email validation error message displayed differently in front end</td><td>Description:
The error message for email validation returned from the back end is displayed differently in the front end. When the user enters an invalid email format, the message shown on the front end does not match the error message sent by the back end. This causes inconsistency between the back-end validation response and the message displayed to the user.
Actual Result:
